- `Shft + SpaceBar` -> For selecting/highlighting the whole row.  
- `Ctrl + SpaceBar` -> For Selecting/highlighting the whole column.  
- `Ctrl + a` or `Shft + SpaceBar` + `Ctrl + SpaceBar` -> For Selecting whole data.  
 
- `Ctrl + home` -> To go to the cell `1st row & 1st column`.  
- `home` -> To go to the `1st cell of the row`.  
- `

- `Ctrl + Shft + L` -> Turn On/Off the filters in the header row for all columns.  
- `Alt + Down Arrow` -> For dropdown filter menu.  
- `
